cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.TL, cs.DS, cs.FL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with proof theoretic analysis of termination principles.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses termination of term rewrite systems.
- cs.TL (Automata Theory and Formal Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with wellfoundedness of recursive path orders.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses complexity analysis of terms.
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also relevant as the paper deals with abstract termination principles.
